<html>
<head>
        <meta charset=UTF-8>
        <title>Error 안내</title>
        <style>
                html,body,dd {margin:0;padding:0}
                html {font-size:16px;}
                body {font-family:"돋움","굴림",Dotum,Gulim,Verdana,sans-serif;}
                a {text-decoration:none}
        .cx-error {margin:72px auto;text-align:center}
                .cx-error .ico-bgError {height:64px;background:url(./images/error/ico_bgError.png) center center no-repeat}
                .cx-error .error-tit,
                .cx-error .error-tit .accent,
                .cx-error .btn-box a {font-family:Noto Sans CJK, Malgun Gothic, Sans-serif;}
                .cx-error .error-tit {margin-bottom:24px;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:500;color:#333;}
                .cx-error .error-tit .accent {color:#0AACBE;vertical-align:baseline}
                .cx-error .error-txt {margin-bottom:24px;font-size:12px;color:#5A5A5A;line-height:1.75}
                .cx-error .btn-box {margin-bottom:40px}
                .cx-error .btn-box a {margin:0 !important;padding:0 10px;height:32px;border:1px solid #0AACBE;box-sizing:border-box;font-size:0.875rem;color:#FFF;line-height:30px;}
                .cx-error .btn-box a,.cx-error .btn-box a:visited {border-color:#0AACBE;background-color:#0AACBE;}
                .cx-error .btn-box a:hover,.cx-error .btn-box a:focus {border-color:#088A98;background-color:#088A98;}
                .cx-error .btn-box a:active {border-color:#077885;background-color:#077885;}
                .cx-error .logo-moef {padding-top:40px;height:27px;border-top:1px solid #CCCCCC;box-sizing:content-box;background:url(./images/error/logo_moef.png) center 40px no-repeat}
        </style>
</head>
<body style="padding:20px;">
<div class="w2group cx-error">
        <div class="w2group ico-bgError"></div>
        <dl class="w2group ">
                <dt class="error-tit">서비스에 <span class="accent">접속할 수 없습니다.</span></dt>
                <dd class="error-txt">죄송합니다. 기술적인 문제로 일시적으로 접속되지 않았습니다.<br/>또는 빌드/배포 중인 경우 잠시 후 다시 접속 하시기 바랍니다.</dd>
        </dl>
        <div class="w2group btn-box">
                <a class="w2anchor2 btn x-large" href="#">문의하러 가기</a>
        </div>
        <div class="w2group logo-moef"></div>
</div>
</body>
